                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-774-18690816 t18690816-774-punishment-74"></join>Fifteen Months' Imprisonment</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HOLMES</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18690816-774-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18690816-774-verdict-3" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18690816-774-verdict-3" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
               </p>
